      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROCK THE NATION NZ (1) resumes off some decent form last time in and is two-time fresh winner. Should be ready to go again having placed in a recent trial and is well served by the ace draw. ABSOLUTE WEAPON (2) added to her consistent form when she came from a wider barrier and finished fourth in a higher-graded race last start at this venue. Has the benefit of a good draw and all three career wins have come at this distance. Looks suited. HALL MOST AN ANGEL (9) draws on the back row this time but should enjoy a nice trail and is hard to knock having made it two wins in succession last start when he got the cash by 1.7 metres at this circuit and distance. ALTA DOWNS (3) is heading the right way, improving last time for second at this circuit and distance. Draws to play a role again. LUCKY ZARA (5) is worth thought off a last-start win at Young.",
